reviewText: I Like Aliens.  I like Cowboys.  And Cowboys AND Aliens are EVEN BETTER!!!!!  Aliens in the Wild, Wild West was REALLy cheeseball but likeable.  Oblivian & Oblivian 2 are the real gems in this set.  Overall a great set of movies

I enjoyed this science fiction triller, it was like a blast from the past, we are so accustomed to watching very sophisticated and elaborate not to mention expensive special effects in all latest action movies, but it's nice to view a 1980's one to remind me of earlier times.
